{"tid":2039500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙男子慘遭商人欺騙 將芫荽當大麻吸食4年","createTime":"2020-05-28T05:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T05:44:22.000Z","uid":297241,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e067b8dedfeab7cc44b540757d4925b2598021ca","tid":2039500,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:11:13.000Z","msg":"西班牙男子慘遭商人欺騙 <br />\n將芫荽當大麻吸食4年 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n芫荽含有豐富的維他素A、B1、B2及C，也有&beta;胡蘿蔔素，兼具營養及調味的雙重好處。不過就不是人人都喜歡它的味道，甚至非常排斥。在西班牙，<span style=\"color: red;\">有一名男子遭到商人欺騙，將芫荽當成大麻吸食了4年，繼而向警方報案</span>，勢要追回買大麻的錢。<br />\n<br />\n一名西班牙28歲的男子，被賣藥的商人欺騙，將芫荽當大麻進食，更吸了4年，他發現後，憤而向警察報案，要將4年的買藥錢全部拿回來。"},{"pid":"a6bbdc215a21fbc939f3ac5f1ea92971c45d694f","tid":2039500,"uid":122134,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"點解要追<br />\n佢用錢買左健康<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9b1321b1fb036ca112b123962e4ff1bc246e50","tid":2039500,"uid":284304,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"吸左成4年先知 死撚左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371c41cdfe45f146eee29dab344a6dad41199fb2","tid":2039500,"uid":38056,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:16:53.000Z","msg":"食完係咪仲扮上晒電咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d1b52f650c86f552c64b21cba65ddb6a26b584","tid":2039500,"uid":187957,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"呢D真係食落喉嚨好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ec9e905e10c3cfc17a40c20eaba03436350335","tid":2039500,"uid":49359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"371c41cdfe45f146eee29dab344a6dad41199fb2","tid":2039500,"uid":38056,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:16:53.000Z","msg":"食完係咪仲扮上晒電咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /